Taylor Johnson
Assistant Golf Professional

Taylor Johnson is a proud native of Council Bluffs, Iowa. With a strong connection to the local community. Taylor is a familiar face here at Whispering Woods

Notably, Taylor recently achieved a significant milestone by graduating from Concordia University in Seward, Nebraska. Taylor's dedication and hard work paid off as he earned a degree in Information Technology, equipping him with the necessary knowledge and skills to thrive in the ever-evolving tech industry.

Looking ahead, Taylor has exciting plans to further develop their professional journey. In September of 2024, he will be embarking on an exciting new chapter by joining the PGA Apprenticeship program. This program will provide Taylor with invaluable opportunities to enhance his abilities and pursue his passion for golf.
